Generated by Crucible v1.0.0 | Theme: soft | Framework: vue

## Variants
- \`default\`- \`primary\`- \`secondary\`- \`outline\`- \`ghost\`- \`link\`- \`destructive\`

## Sizes
- \`xs\`- \`sm\`- \`md\`- \`lg\`- \`icon\`

## States
